{"segment":2,"line_start":101,"line_end":200,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_lv_bu_wei","speaker_name":"吕不韦","listener":"char_xiao_pan","text":"比武助兴，既可增添热闹，更可显扬我大秦武风，请储君示准。","tone":"陈述","chapter":205,"line_start":120,"line_end":121},{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":"char_lao_ai","text":"嫪卿家会派出哪位剑手来让我们一开眼界？","tone":"疑问","chapter":205,"line_start":128,"line_end":129},{"speaker":"char_han_jie","speaker_name":"韩竭","listener":"char_xiao_pan","text":"内史府客卿韩竭，请太后、储君赐准献技。","tone":"沉声","chapter":205,"line_start":132,"line_end":133},{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":"char_zhu_ji","text":"一切由太后作主。","tone":"陈述","chapter":205,"line_start":142,"line_end":142},{"speaker":"char_zhu_ji","speaker_name":"朱姬","listener":null,"text":"韩竭乃有'稷下剑圣'之称的忘忧先生曹秋道的得意门生，剑法超群，不过仲父手下能人无数，必可派出人选，好逼得韩先生抖出绝艺，让我等见识一二。","tone":"温柔","chapter":205,"line_start":146,"line_end":147},{"speaker":"char_teng_yi","speaker_name":"滕翼","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"真想去把韩竭的龟卵子捏他娘的出来。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":205,"line_start":150,"line_end":151},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_teng_yi","text":"二哥总有机会的，何不现在藉吕不韦的人，看看这龟卵子有何本领。","tone":"调侃","chapter":205,"line_start":154,"line_end":155},{"speaker":"char_jing_jun","speaker_name":"荆俊","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"吕贼必会派许商出来，除他和管中邪外，怕没有人是这龟卵子的对手。","tone":"认真","chapter":205,"line_start":158,"line_end":159},{"speaker":"char_lv_bu_wei","speaker_name":"吕不韦","listener":"char_lian_jiao","text":"好！记着点到即止。","tone":"大笑","chapter":205,"line_start":172,"line_end":172},{"speaker":"char_teng_yi","speaker_name":"滕翼","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"这小子与善柔同出一门，为何剑路上却完全不同呢？","tone":"好奇","chapter":205,"line_start":190,"line_end":191},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_teng_yi","text":"只从曹秋道能调教出两个不同的徒弟出来，可知曹秋道确已达大宗师级的境界。","tone":"陈述","chapter":205,"line_start":194,"line_end":195}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_han_jie","name":"韩竭